SLIDE 1: AMAZON S3 â€“ ADVANCED (TITLE)
================================================================================

Overview:
---------
This section covers advanced Amazon S3 features for optimization, automation,
performance, and analytics.

Topics Covered:
- Moving Between Storage Classes
- Lifecycle Rules
- S3 Analytics
- Requester Pays
- Event Notifications
- Performance Optimization
- Batch Operations
- Storage Lens

================================================================================
SLIDE 2: AMAZON S3 â€“ MOVING BETWEEN STORAGE CLASSES
================================================================================

Transition Capabilities:
------------------------
â€¢ You can TRANSITION objects between storage classes
â€¢ Transitions follow a waterfall model (can go down, not up)

Storage Class Hierarchy (Top to Bottom):
----------------------------------------
